2338
02:13:07,814 --> 02:13:10,483
They just suffered a slight setback.

2339
02:13:10,567 --> 02:13:13,278
And after all, "what is a man profited

2340
02:13:13,361 --> 02:13:17,615
"if he shall gain Maryland
and lose the entire south?"

2341
02:13:18,825 --> 02:13:21,703
Matthew, chapter 16, verse 26.

2342
02:13:23,454 --> 02:13:24,664
Mcnair.

2343
02:13:25,331 --> 02:13:27,166
I know. The flies.

2344
02:13:27,250 --> 02:13:28,293
No.

2345
02:13:29,210 --> 02:13:30,461
The rum.

2346
02:13:35,091 --> 02:13:37,885
Well, what are we all sitting around for?

2347
02:13:39,262 --> 02:13:40,972
We're wasting time. Precious time.

2348
02:13:41,055 --> 02:13:43,141
Thomas, I want you
to ride down into Delaware

2349
02:13:43,224 --> 02:13:44,851
and fetch back Caesar Rodney.

2350
02:13:44,934 --> 02:13:48,271
John, are you mad?
It's 80 miles, and he's a dying man.

2351
02:13:48,354 --> 02:13:50,398
No, he's a patriot.

2352
02:13:50,481 --> 02:13:52,859
John, what good will it do?
The south's done us in.

2353
02:13:52,942 --> 02:13:54,569
And suppose they change their minds?

2354
02:13:54,652 --> 02:13:57,155
Can we get Delaware without Rodney?

2355
02:13:59,907 --> 02:14:02,952
God! What a bastardly bunch we are.

2356
02:14:05,496 --> 02:14:08,750
- Stephen, I want you to...
- L'm going to the tavern, Johnny.

2357
02:14:08,833 --> 02:14:12,378
If there's anything I can do for you there,
let me know.

2358
02:14:13,296 --> 02:14:14,464
Chase.

2359
02:14:15,340 --> 02:14:16,424
Bartlett!

2360
02:14:16,507 --> 02:14:20,094
What's the use, John?
The vote's tomorrow morning.

2361
02:14:20,178 --> 02:14:22,597
There's less than a full day left.

2362
02:14:25,975 --> 02:14:27,518
Roger.

2363
02:14:27,602 --> 02:14:30,104
Face facts, John. It's finished.

2364
02:14:32,857 --> 02:14:34,442
I'm sorry, John.

2365
02:14:42,825 --> 02:14:44,786
We have no choice, John.

2366
02:14:45,953 --> 02:14:47,789
The slavery clause has got to go.

2367
02:14:51,042 --> 02:14:52,460
Franklin, what are you saying?

2368
02:14:52,960 --> 02:14:54,754
It's a luxury we can't afford.

2369
02:14:55,880 --> 02:14:57,131
A luxury?

2370
02:14:59,550 --> 02:15:03,304
A half million souls in chains,

2371
02:15:03,388 --> 02:15:06,391
and Dr. Franklin calls it a luxury.

2372
02:15:07,517 --> 02:15:09,394
Maybe you should've
walked out with the south.

2373
02:15:09,936 --> 02:15:11,896
You forget yourself, sir.

2374
02:15:11,979 --> 02:15:15,149
I founded the first anti-slavery society
on this continent.

2375
02:15:15,608 --> 02:15:18,903
Don't wave your credentials at me.
Perhaps it's time you had them renewed.

2376
02:15:19,529 --> 02:15:22,573
The issue here is independence.

2377
02:15:22,657 --> 02:15:25,451
Perhaps you've forgotten that fact,
but I have not.

2378
02:15:25,535 --> 02:15:29,080
How dare you jeopardize our cause

2379
02:15:29,163 --> 02:15:31,082
when we've come so far!

2380
02:15:32,709 --> 02:15:34,043
These men,

2381
02:15:35,336 --> 02:15:37,588
no matter how much
we may disagree with them,

2382
02:15:37,672 --> 02:15:41,092
are not ribbon clerks to be ordered about.

2383
02:15:41,175 --> 02:15:44,387
They're proud, accomplished men.
The cream of their colonies.

2384
02:15:44,470 --> 02:15:47,473
And whether you like it or not,
they and the people they represent

2385
02:15:47,557 --> 02:15:51,436
will be part of this new nation
you hope to create.

2386
02:15:51,519 --> 02:15:54,731
Now either learn how to live with them
or pack up and go home.

2387
02:16:00,361 --> 02:16:03,448
In any case,
stop acting like a Boston fishwife.

2388
02:16:17,545 --> 02:16:20,423
Good god. What's happened to me?

2389
02:16:20,506 --> 02:16:23,801
John Adams. The great John Adams.

2390
02:16:24,302 --> 02:16:25,845
What have I come to?

2391
02:16:25,928 --> 02:16:27,805
Law practice down the pipe.

2392
02:16:27,889 --> 02:16:30,016
Farm mortgaged to the hilt.

2393
02:16:30,099 --> 02:16:33,227
At a stage in life when other men prosper,

2394
02:16:33,311 --> 02:16:35,938
I'm reduced to living in Philadelphia.

2395
02:16:37,982 --> 02:16:39,442
Philadelphia.

2396
02:16:48,826 --> 02:16:51,412
Abigail, what am I going to do?

2397
02:16:51,496 --> 02:16:52,747
<i>Do, John?</i>

2398
02:16:54,081 --> 02:16:55,750
